      "title": "The President leaves the Parliament amidst the protests of the opposition members",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The opposition members of the Parliament strongly objected to President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa who came to join the Parliament session.",
        "As soon as the Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe's statement ended, the opposition MPs started protesting and the President left the Parliament amid the protests."
